00:00:32.460 --> 00:00:34.890
thinking about abstractions that
we can use for thinking

00:00:34.890 --> 00:00:36.690
about circuits.

00:00:36.690 --> 00:00:40.220
The attractions are things that
capitalize on linearity.

00:00:40.220 --> 00:00:42.560
And they include things like
